            , in Windford-Street.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Did not you swear before the Justice that you had this Butter from a Carman ?</p>
               <p>Lightfoot. Yes, I did so. But ah! you threatened my Life if I swore it against you.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17320223-14-person118">
                  Samuel 
                  Isaac 
               <interp inst="t17320223-14-person118" type="surname" value="Isaac"></interp>
