                  </persName>
            , Carter's Boy. Lightfoot brought some Firkins to our House, and my Master bought them of him.</p>
               <p>Mr. Colebrant. We lost Butter 3 or 4 times while the Prisoner lived with me, which was about 11 Months, but he constantly deny'd it, and I can't say but that he behaved very well in my Service.</p>
               <p>
            
